# Reddit OAuth Credentials
#
# To register your personal app:
# 1. Go to https://reddit.com/prefs/apps
# 2. Click "Create App" or "Create Another App"
# 3. Select "Installed App" (script type)
# 4. Fill in the form:
#    - Name: RedMan (or anything)
#    - App type: Installed app
#    - Redirect URI: http://localhost:7895/oauth/callback
# 5. Copy the client ID and client secret below
#
# This file should NOT be committed to git.
# Create a .env.local file with your actual credentials.

REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here
